Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.57,0:00:26.69,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( violin music playing )
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.51,0:00:53.05,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( inaudible )
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.10,0:01:05.65,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( inaudible )
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.15,0:01:10.07,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( inaudible )
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.07,0:01:14.87,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( Minami speaking\Nin German accent )
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.95,0:01:16.87,Main,,0,0,0,,I'M GOING TO JAPAN.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.83,0:01:23.25,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( theme music playing )\N- ( singing in Japanese )
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.96,0:02:54.88,Main,,0,0,0,,- Minami: IT WAS A\NYEAR AGO TODAY,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.97,0:02:57.80,Main,,0,0,0,,DURING THE\NORIENTATION CEREMONY.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.89,0:02:59.80,Main,,0,0,0,,I'D JUST MOVED TO JAPAN\NFROM GERMANY,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.89,0:03:03.31,Main,,0,0,0,,SO I WASN'T VERY FAMILIAR\NWITH THE LANGUAGE YET.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.39,0:03:05.94,Main,,0,0,0,,- NICE TO MEET YOU, AND I HOPE\NYOU HAVE A GOOD YEAR.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:09.77,Main,,0,0,0,,- "IF I WANT TO FIT IN HERE,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.86,0:03:11.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I HAVE TO MAKE A GOOD\NFIRST IMPRESSION.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.65,0:03:13.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I CAN'T GO UP THERE\NAND EMBARRASS MYSELF.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.24,0:03:18.16,Main,,0,0,0,,NO GETTING NERVOUS\NOR FIDGETY
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.24,0:03:20.32,Main,,0,0,0,,AND MAKING EVERYONE THINK\NI'M CRAZY."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.41,0:03:21.99,Main,,0,0,0,,THOSE WERE THE SORTS OF THINGS\NGOING THROUGH MY HEAD
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.08,0:03:25.79,Main,,0,0,0,,AS I WAITED MY TURN TO INTRODUCE\NMYSELF TO THE CLASS.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.79,0:03:30.84,Main,,0,0,0,,- Fukuhara: NEXT WE HAVE\NMINAMI SHIMADA.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.14,0:03:46.48,Main,,0,0,0,,- HELLO EVERYONE, MY NAME\NIS MINAMI SHIMADA.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:50.02,Main,,0,0,0,,IT'S SO NICE TO\NTHANK YOU ALL SO MUCH.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.10,0:03:52.23,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( students murmuring )
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.31,0:03:54.23,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT HAPPENED?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.32,0:03:58.32,Main,,0,0,0,,DID I DO SOMETHING\NSTRANGE ALREADY?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.41,0:04:01.70,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'VE BEEN TOLD MISS SHIMADA IS\NA RETURNEE STUDENT FROM GERMANY.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.78,0:04:05.70,Main,,0,0,0,,I IMAGINE IT'LL BE DIFFICULT\NFOR HER TO ADJUST FOR A WHILE.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.79,0:04:08.54,Main,,0,0,0,,THERE ARE A LOT OF THINGS IN\NJAPAN SHE'S STILL NOT USED TO,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.62,0:04:11.33,Main,,0,0,0,,SO DO YOUR BEST\NTO HELP HER OUT.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.42,0:04:13.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I KNOW IT SEEMS DIFFICULT,\NBUT TAKE IT SLOW.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.42,0:04:15.34,Main,,0,0,0,,IF YOU'RE GOING TO USE\NCHINESE KANJI,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.42,0:04:16.63,Main,,0,0,0,,START WITH ONE CHARACTER\NAT A TIME.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.71,0:04:18.30,Main,,0,0,0,,- CHINESE?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.48,0:04:30.48,Main,,0,0,0,,IT'S NICE TO MEET YOU\NSO MUCH.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.02,0:04:34.15,Main,,0,0,0,,EMBARRASSING.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.23,0:04:35.27,Main,,0,0,0,,WHY DIDN'T THEY JUST TELL ME I\NWAS WRITING IT WRONG
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.36,0:04:37.40,Main,,0,0,0,,INSTEAD OF STARING?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.49,0:04:40.61,Main,,0,0,0,,- Minami: MY DAD HAD TOLD ME\NEVERYONE IN JAPAN WOULD BE NICE,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.70,0:04:43.03,Main,,0,0,0,,AND THAT I'D BE ABLE TO\NMAKE FRIENDS SUPER EASY.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.12,0:04:45.58,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT THAT ONE CLASS PROVED HIM\NWRONG IN THIRTY SECONDS.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.66,0:04:47.00,Main,,0,0,0,,I FELT LIKE CRAP.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.38,0:04:56.63,Main,,0,0,0,,- HEY, MY NAME'S YUUJI SAKAMOTO.\NREALLY GLAD TO BE HERE.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.71,0:04:59.05,Main,,0,0,0,,- THAT'S THE ONE EVERYONE CALLED\N"THE DEMON" AT HIS OLD SCHOOL,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.13,0:05:00.68,Main,,0,0,0,,AND I CAN SEE WHY.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.76,0:05:02.18,Main,,0,0,0,,- DO YOU THINK IT'S TOO LATE\NTO SWITCH CLASSES?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.56,0:05:08.10,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( German accent ) HAVE I COME\NTO A SCHOOL OF DELINQUENTS?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.18,0:05:09.89,Main,,0,0,0,,NO, NO, NO.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.98,0:05:12.31,Main,,0,0,0,,FATHER SAID\NJAPAN IS VERY SAFE,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.39,0:05:15.98,Main,,0,0,0,,SO I AM SURE HE IS NOT AS\NSCARY AS HE LOOKS.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.03,0:05:25.24,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'M HIDEYOSHI KINOSHITA.\NIT'S NICE TO MEET ALL OF YOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:28.87,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH MY.  IS THIS GIRL\NREALLY WEARING A BOY'S UNIFORM?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.95,0:05:33.33,Main,,0,0,0,,MAYBE SHE'S ONE OF THOSE GIRLS\NWHO ISN'T INTO WEARING SKIRTS.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.42,0:05:35.08,Main,,0,0,0,,AND THAT IS OKAY.\NIT'S NOT WEIRD AT ALL.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.17,0:05:38.21,Main,,0,0,0,,DAD SAID THERE IS NOTHING\NSTRANGE OR SCARY ABOUT JAPAN,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.30,0:05:39.92,Main,,0,0,0,,AND HE IS RIGHT.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.89,0:05:48.68,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'M KOUTA TSUCHIYA,\NAND I TAKE PIC--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.76,0:05:49.89,Main,,0,0,0,,PICNIC LUNCHES.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.97,0:05:51.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I'M VERY GOOD AT STALKI--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.43,0:05:52.69,Main,,0,0,0,,UH, NOT GOOD AT ANYTHING.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.19,0:05:58.40,Main,,0,0,0,,- PLEASE WAIT, THERE IS\NSOMETHING YOU DROPPED.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.44,0:06:03.74,Main,,0,0,0,,- FORGET WHAT YOU SAW\NIF YOU KNOW WHAT'S GOOD FOR YOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.87,0:06:07.99,Main,,0,0,0,,- OKAY, THAT WAS NOT CREEPY.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.08,0:06:10.62,Main,,0,0,0,,HE USES THAT CAMERA\NTO RECORD THE CLASSES.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.70,0:06:12.91,Main,,0,0,0,,NOTHING STRANGE.\NJUST LIKE FATHER SAID.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.80,0:06:22.92,Main,,0,0,0,,- AND NOW STRAIGHT FROM\NNAGATSUI JUNIOR HIGH,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.01,0:06:26.14,Main,,0,0,0,,THE ONE AND ONLY,\NAKIHISA YOSHII!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.22,0:06:28.35,Main,,0,0,0,,( laughs )
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.43,0:06:29.72,Main,,0,0,0,,- THAT KID IS STRANGE.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.81,0:06:31.60,Main,,0,0,0,,THEY'RE ALL FREAKS!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.68,0:06:33.69,Main,,0,0,0,,FATHER LIED TO ME!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.77,0:06:36.10,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( students chattering )
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.19,0:06:38.52,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU'RE A RETURNEE STUDENT?\NTHAT'S SO COOL.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.61,0:06:39.61,Main,,0,0,0,,- HEY, WHEN DID YOU GET BACK\NTO JAPAN?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.69,0:06:41.69,Main,,0,0,0,,- WERE YOU BORN IN GERMANY?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.78,0:06:44.53,Main,,0,0,0,,- Minami: LIKE THEY'D NEVER\NSEEN A RETURNEE STUDENT.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:45.95,Main,,0,0,0,,EITHER THEY WERE\NHONESTLY INTERESTED
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.03,0:06:47.49,Main,,0,0,0,,OR TOTALLY FREAKED OUT.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.57,0:06:49.24,Main,,0,0,0,,- ARE YOU, LIKE,\NREALLY GOOD AT GERMAN?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.32,0:06:51.20,Main,,0,0,0,,- ARE YOU GONNA JOIN A CLUB\NAT THIS SCHOOL?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.29,0:06:53.12,Main,,0,0,0,,- DID YOU HAVE A BOYFRIEND\NON THE OTHER SIDE?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.20,0:06:55.33,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( German accent )\NI CAN'T UNDERSTAND THEM.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.42,0:06:56.71,Main,,0,0,0,,THEY'RE ALL TALKING SO FAST,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.79,0:06:58.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I CAN BARELY PICK\NUP A FEW WORDS.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.04,0:07:01.17,Main,,0,0,0,,I DON'T REMEMBER IF IT'S\N"PLEASE SLOW DOWN"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:03.05,Main,,0,0,0,,OR "PLEASE BE QUIET."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.13,0:07:04.38,Main,,0,0,0,,- DO YOU KNOW WHAT CATS ARE?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.47,0:07:05.93,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT DO PEOPLE EAT OVER THERE?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.01,0:07:07.09,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT SIZE BRA DO YOU WEAR?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.85,0:07:10.18,Main,,0,0,0,,- WAIT A MINUTE.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.26,0:07:11.60,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAT DID THAT GIRL SAY\NTHIS MORNING
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.68,0:07:12.60,Main,,0,0,0,,THAT MADE THOSE GUYS BACK UP?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:15.06,Main,,0,0,0,,IT WAS JUST ONE PHRASE.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.14,0:07:18.52,Main,,0,0,0,,OH, YAH.\NI REMEMBER NOW.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.61,0:07:20.48,Main,,0,0,0,,DA...\N- All: DA?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.56,0:07:23.40,Main,,0,0,0,,- DAMN STUPID PIGS.\NSHUT YOUR FAT TRAPS.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.49,0:07:25.82,Main,,0,0,0,,- All: UH...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.90,0:07:27.74,Main,,0,0,0,,- UH?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.79,0:07:33.91,Main,,0,0,0,,- Minami: NEEDLESS TO SAY,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.00,0:07:37.21,Main,,0,0,0,,THAT DID NOT MAKE A\NGOOD FIRST IMPRESSION.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.29,0:07:39.17,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( students chattering )
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:41.00,Main,,0,0,0,,- I ASKED DAD ABOUT IT LATER.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.09,0:07:42.84,Main,,0,0,0,,TURNS OUT IT'S NOT\NTHE NICEST THING TO SAY
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.92,0:07:44.38,Main,,0,0,0,,TO PEOPLE YOU WANT\NTO LIKE YOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.46,0:07:47.05,Main,,0,0,0,,AFTER THAT,\NTHEY WERE SCARED.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.13,0:07:49.30,Main,,0,0,0,,NONE OF THEM EVEN WANTED TO\NCOME CLOSE TO ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.39,0:07:52.60,Main,,0,0,0,,WELL, EXCEPT FOR ONE PERSON.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.68,0:07:55.02,Main,,0,0,0,,- EXCUSE ME.\NSHIMADA, RIGHT?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.10,0:07:57.81,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH, HI!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.89,0:08:01.81,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( squeaking )
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.90,0:08:04.11,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( sighs )\N- WHAT?!  WHAT'D I DO?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.19,0:08:07.28,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( German accent ) DO YOU ALL\NTHE TIME WEAR THOSE TO SCHOOL?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:10.28,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU MEAN THE SAILOR SUIT?\NNO, I OVERSLEPT.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.37,0:08:12.87,Main,,0,0,0,,AND I DIDN'T HAVE\NANYMORE TIME.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.95,0:08:14.70,Main,,0,0,0,,I JUST GRABBED SOMETHING\NAND RAN OUT.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.79,0:08:17.12,Main,,0,0,0,,- SO BEING IN A HURRY\NMADE IT OKAY
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:19.37,Main,,0,0,0,,TO DRESS UP\NIN A SAILOR COSTUME?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.46,0:08:21.38,Main,,0,0,0,,IF THIS IS HOW\NJAPANESE STUDENTS THINK,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.46,0:08:23.13,Main,,0,0,0,,I'LL NEVER FIGURE\NTHIS PLACE OUT.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.21,0:08:24.63,Main,,0,0,0,,- HEY, ARE YOU GONNA MOVE?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.71,0:08:26.26,Main,,0,0,0,,OR ARE YOU JUST GONNA KEEP\NBLOCKING THE EXIT
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.34,0:08:27.67,Main,,0,0,0,,AND RAMBLING ON LIKE AN IDIOT?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.76,0:08:29.51,Main,,0,0,0,,- THERE IS NO NEED TO BE RUDE,\NBUDDY!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.59,0:08:31.85,Main,,0,0,0,,SHIMADA'S JUST NOT USED TO\NLIVING IN JAPAN YET, OKAY?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.93,0:08:33.35,Main,,0,0,0,,THAT DOESN'T MAKE HER AN IDIOT.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.43,0:08:35.47,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH, SHUT UP!\NI WAS TALKING TO YOU, STUPID.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.56,0:08:37.60,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH, YEAH?  WELL, WHAT'S\NSO STUPID ABOUT ME?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.68,0:08:39.39,Main,,0,0,0,,- EVERYTHING!  AND WHOSE\NDRESS ARE YOU WEARING?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.48,0:08:41.40,Main,,0,0,0,,- IT'S A SHIRT,\NAND YOU SHOULDN'T JUDGE PEOPLE
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.48,0:08:42.73,Main,,0,0,0,,BY WHO THEY ARE\NOR WHAT THEY'RE WEARING!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.81,0:08:44.11,Main,,0,0,0,,- HOW ELSE AM I GONNA\NJUDGE THEM?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.19,0:08:45.77,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU'RE NOT MAKING ANY SENSE,\NDUDE.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.86,0:08:47.24,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHATEVER!\NYOU'RE STUPID TOO.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.32,0:08:49.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I SAW IT WITH MY OWN EYES!\NTHIS MORNING!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:50.99,Main,,0,0,0,,THAT REALLY PRETTY GIRL\NTRIED TO TALK TO YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.07,0:08:53.03,Main,,0,0,0,,AND YOU JUST IGNORED HER\NLIKE A TURD.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.12,0:08:54.45,Main,,0,0,0,,- THAT'S NONE OF YOUR BUSINESS.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.53,0:08:55.87,Main,,0,0,0,,AND WHY WERE YOU STARING\NIN THE FIRST PLACE?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.95,0:08:57.45,Main,,0,0,0,,I KNEW THERE WAS SOMETHING\NWRONG WITH YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.54,0:08:59.21,Main,,0,0,0,,FROM THE VERY FIRST TIME\NI SAW YOUR STUPID ASS.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:00.96,Main,,0,0,0,,- I COULD SAY THE SAME TO YOU!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.04,0:09:03.38,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAT KIND OF DILL WEED CALLS\NSOMEONE THEY JUST MET AN IDIOT?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.46,0:09:04.75,Main,,0,0,0,,ONLY A LUNATIC, THAT'S WHO!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.84,0:09:06.13,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH, NO WAY!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.21,0:09:07.84,Main,,0,0,0,,SAILOR SISSY BOY IS\NCALLING ME CRAZY?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.92,0:09:09.34,Main,,0,0,0,,WHY DON'T YOU GIVE THAT\NCIRCUS MONKEY BACK HIS OUTFIT?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.42,0:09:11.88,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'M GOING TO GOOD-BYE.\NTHANK YOU SO MUCH.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.89,0:09:17.22,Main,,0,0,0,,- Minami: I DIDN'T UNDERSTAND\NEVERYTHING THEY WERE SAYING,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.31,0:09:19.52,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT I GOT THE IDEA I SHOULD\NPROBABLY GO AHEAD
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.60,0:09:20.89,Main,,0,0,0,,AND AVOID THEM.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.98,0:09:22.81,Main,,0,0,0,,I WAS TRYING TO GET BACK TO\NA NORMAL SCHOOL LIFE,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.90,0:09:25.48,Main,,0,0,0,,NOT CREATE MORE DRAMA\NFOR MYSELF.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.57,0:09:27.40,Main,,0,0,0,,THINGS WERE GREAT IN GERMANY.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.48,0:09:29.11,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT HAZUKI, MY LITTLE SISTER?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.19,0:09:30.61,Main,,0,0,0,,SHE NEEDED ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:32.49,Main,,0,0,0,,SHE'S WHY I CAME BACK\NTO JAPAN WITH DAD
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.57,0:09:34.03,Main,,0,0,0,,WHEN HE GOT HIS JOB TRANSFER.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.12,0:09:37.37,Main,,0,0,0,,STILL, I WASN'T SURE\NI DID THE RIGHT THING.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.83,0:09:42.08,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( German accent )\NSO THE GIRLS' ROOM IS BLUE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.16,0:09:44.71,Main,,0,0,0,,AND THE BOYS' IS PINK HERE,\NIS IT?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.79,0:09:47.92,Main,,0,0,0,,YES, THAT COULD HAVE BEEN\NVERY AWKWARD.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:50.38,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( boys screaming )
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.47,0:09:52.76,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT THE HELL?!\NWHY ARE THERE GIRLS IN HERE?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.84,0:09:54.55,Main,,0,0,0,,- Hideyoshi: WHERE?\NI AM NOT A GIRL!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.64,0:09:56.89,Main,,0,0,0,,- COME RIGHT HERE,\NKINOSHITA!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.97,0:09:58.31,Main,,0,0,0,,- NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.39,0:10:00.06,Main,,0,0,0,,I HAVE TO PEE REALLY BAD!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.14,0:10:01.60,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( both pant )
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.68,0:10:03.27,Main,,0,0,0,,- I DON'T UNDERSTAND.\NWHY DID I HAVE TO LEAVE?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.35,0:10:07.90,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( shouts in German )
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.98,0:10:10.03,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT ARE YOU SAYING?\NWHY ARE YOU SO MAD?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.11,0:10:11.74,Main,,0,0,0,,I'M SORRY ABOUT ALL THIS,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:13.78,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT I'M NOT THE ONE WHO WALKED\NINTO THE WRONG RESTROOM.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.86,0:10:15.49,Main,,0,0,0,,SHIMADA, WAIT!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.24,0:10:19.79,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( German accent )\NI KNOW IT'S JUST THE FIRST DAY,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.87,0:10:22.41,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT EVERYTHING ABOUT JAPAN\NIS FREAKING ME OUT.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.50,0:10:25.04,Main,,0,0,0,,I'M SURE IT'LL START TO MAKE\NSENSE EVENTUALLY.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.13,0:10:26.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I JUST HAVE TO BE PATIENT
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.58,0:10:28.92,Main,,0,0,0,,AND PUT UP WITH A BIT\NOF CRAZINESS UNTIL THEN.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.00,0:10:32.05,Main,,0,0,0,,AT LEAST I GET TO SPEND\NSOME MORE TIME WITH MY FAMILY.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.13,0:10:34.09,Main,,0,0,0,,- JUST A LITTLE HIGHER--\NAAH!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.17,0:10:35.30,Main,,0,0,0,,- YES.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.38,0:10:38.14,Main,,0,0,0,,JAPAN DEFINITELY\NFREAKS ME OUT.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.18,0:10:46.31,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( violin music playing )
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.49,0:10:56.03,Main,,0,0,0,,- Minami: THERE WERE\NONLY STRANGE PEOPLE, EVER.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.62,0:11:05.37,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( inaudible )
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.46,0:11:06.42,Main,,0,0,0,,( German accent )\NFRIENDS.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.17,0:11:12.13,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( dog barking )
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.76,0:11:19.51,Main,,0,0,0,,- Minami:\NBAKA AND TEST!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.18,0:11:26.23,Main,,0,0,0,,CLASSES WERE IN FULL\NSWING AFTER ABOUT A WEEK.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.31,0:11:29.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I WAS OVERWHELMED WITH HOW\NQUICKLY IT WAS MOVING.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.86,0:11:32.98,Main,,0,0,0,,MODERN JAPANESE CLASS WAS HARDER\NTHAN ANY OTHER CLASS I HAD.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.07,0:11:35.99,Main,,0,0,0,,EVERYONE WAS FLUENT,\NAND I COULD BARELY FOLLOW ALONG.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.07,0:11:37.86,Main,,0,0,0,,WHEN THE TIME CAME TO\NREAD CLASSICS,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.95,0:11:39.45,Main,,0,0,0,,IT WAS PRETTY MUCH GIBBERISH.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:41.45,Main,,0,0,0,,- ALL RIGHT,\NTHEN HOW ABOUT YOSHII?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.53,0:11:42.79,Main,,0,0,0,,IN THIS CASE, CAN YOU TELL ME
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.87,0:11:44.87,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAT THE CONJUGATION OF THE\NWORD "HA-BERRY" IS?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.95,0:11:47.21,Main,,0,0,0,,- YES.\NIT'S "HANNARI," SIR.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.29,0:11:50.84,Main,,0,0,0,,- NOW WHY WOULD YOU GIVE ME\NA WORD IN THE KYOTO DIALECT
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.92,0:11:52.46,Main,,0,0,0,,WHEN I ASKED YOU\NFOR THE CONJUGATION
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:54.25,Main,,0,0,0,,OF A CLASSIC JAPANESE WORD?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.34,0:11:56.26,Main,,0,0,0,,IT'S SO IRRELEVANT\NTHAT IT'S ACTUALLY REFRESHING.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.34,0:11:58.18,Main,,0,0,0,,- HUH?\NWHAT DOES THAT EVEN MEAN?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.26,0:11:59.84,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( laughter )
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.39,0:12:05.52,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( chuckles )
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.60,0:12:06.77,Main,,0,0,0,,HUH?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.94,0:12:12.27,Main,,0,0,0,,- THAT'S ALL.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.36,0:12:14.11,Main,,0,0,0,,MAKE SURE YOU'RE FAMILIAR WITH\NEVERYTHING WE DID TODAY
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.19,0:12:15.28,Main,,0,0,0,,BEFORE OUR NEXT CLASS.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.36,0:12:17.86,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( German accent )\NIT'S FINALLY OVER.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.95,0:12:19.86,Main,,0,0,0,,- Minami: I MAY HAVE\NBEEN FREED FROM THE JAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.95,0:12:22.62,Main,,0,0,0,,OF THE MOST BORING\NCLASS EVER, BUT...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.70,0:12:25.45,Main,,0,0,0,,- HEY! WAIT UP, SHIMADA!\NWHERE ARE YOU HEADED NOW?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.54,0:12:28.66,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHERE AM I GO?\N- UM, YEAH, RIGHT.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.75,0:12:30.63,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT IS IT TO SAY\N"TO GO HOME"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.71,0:12:33.29,Main,,0,0,0,,- DID YOU SAY, "WHAT A SEA"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.38,0:12:35.17,Main,,0,0,0,,- TO.  GO.  HOME!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.25,0:12:37.13,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( distorted ) OH, "HOME."\NTHAT MAKES MORE SENSE.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.22,0:12:38.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I THOUGHT YOU WERE\NSAYING SOMETHING
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.38,0:12:39.84,Main,,0,0,0,,ABOUT "THE SEA" FOR A SEC.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.93,0:12:42.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I'M SORRY.  IT'S HARD\NTO UNDERSTAND YOU SOMETIMES.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.14,0:12:43.39,Main,,0,0,0,,GUESS THAT'S WHAT YOU GET\NFOR BEING CULTURED
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.47,0:12:45.22,Main,,0,0,0,,AND STUDYING ABROAD, HUH?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.31,0:12:46.98,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU'RE LIKE A FOREIGNER NOW,\NYOU EVER THOUGHT ABOUT THAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.77,0:12:56.90,Main,,0,0,0,,- Minami: GETTING USED TO A\NLANGUAGE AGAIN IS HARD ENOUGH
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.99,0:12:59.11,Main,,0,0,0,,WHEN PEOPLE SPEAK IT\NAT LIGHTNING SPEED...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.20,0:13:01.99,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT I WAS SO STRESSED OUT\NTHAT I COULDN'T CONCENTRATE.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.07,0:13:03.45,Main,,0,0,0,,MY HEAD WAS POUNDING
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.53,0:13:05.53,Main,,0,0,0,,AND MY BRAIN COULDN'T EVEN\NPROCESS WHAT I WAS HEARING.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.62,0:13:08.20,Main,,0,0,0,,- BELIEVE ME, I WISH\NI COULD DITCH THIS PLACE TOO.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.29,0:13:09.58,Main,,0,0,0,,I'M DYING OF BOREDOM HERE.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.66,0:13:11.75,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT WE STILL GOTTA GO BACK\NTO HOMEROOM AFTER THIS.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.83,0:13:13.34,Main,,0,0,0,,- HUH?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.42,0:13:14.63,Main,,0,0,0,,- I GUESS YOU COULD SHORTEN IT
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.71,0:13:16.17,Main,,0,0,0,,AND CALL IT HOME IF YOU WANTED.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.25,0:13:17.50,Main,,0,0,0,,THEN IT WOULD BE\NTRUE FOR EVERYONE.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.59,0:13:18.51,Main,,0,0,0,,HOW WEIRD WOULD IT BE\NIF WE ALL SAID
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.59,0:13:20.80,Main,,0,0,0,,WE WERE GOING HOME...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.88,0:13:22.80,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT IS HE SMILING ABOUT?\NIS IT REALLY THAT FUNNY THAT
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.89,0:13:26.43,Main,,0,0,0,,I CAN'T SPEAK MY OWN LANGUAGE\NVERY WELL?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.51,0:13:29.14,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( speaks French badly )
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.23,0:13:33.06,Main,,0,0,0,,- HUH?\N- UH...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.15,0:13:36.77,Main,,0,0,0,,( speaks French badly )
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.86,0:13:38.61,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.69,0:13:41.61,Main,,0,0,0,,"TUNA SOMETHING,\NSOMETHING MONAMIE"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.70,0:13:43.74,Main,,0,0,0,,WHY IS HE TALKING ABOUT FISH?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.82,0:13:45.58,Main,,0,0,0,,HE'S JUST SPOUTING OFF\NGIBBERISH.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.66,0:13:47.70,Main,,0,0,0,,AND ON TOP OF THAT, HE'S NOT\NEVEN SAYING MY NAME RIGHT.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.79,0:13:52.00,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( speaks French badly )
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.13,0:14:00.13,Main,,0,0,0,,- PLEASE STOP!\NI DO NOT KNOW!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.22,0:14:01.42,Main,,0,0,0,,- UH--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.30,0:14:08.06,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( crying )
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.14,0:14:11.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I DON'T KNOW WHAT TO DO.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.98,0:14:13.77,Main,,0,0,0,,THIS IS SO HARD.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.85,0:14:16.82,Main,,0,0,0,,WHY DOESN'T ANYONE\NUNDERSTAND ME?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.90,0:14:20.44,Main,,0,0,0,,IT'S NOT LIKE\NI'M NOT TRYING.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.53,0:14:23.07,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAT IF--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.15,0:14:25.74,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAT IF THEY ALL HATE ME NOW?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.82,0:14:26.74,Main,,0,0,0,,( inaudible )
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.83,0:14:27.99,Main,,0,0,0,,IT WAS A MISTAKE.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.08,0:14:30.41,Main,,0,0,0,,I NEVER SHOULD HAVE\NCOME BACK HERE.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.08,0:14:37.42,Main,,0,0,0,,I WON'T TO GO HOME.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.50,0:14:38.71,Main,,0,0,0,,( crying )
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.81,0:14:55.23,Main,,0,0,0,,- Minami:\NNOTHING HAD CHANGED.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.31,0:14:57.65,Main,,0,0,0,,I STILL COULDN'T FOLLOW ALONG\NIN CLASS.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.73,0:14:59.61,Main,,0,0,0,,I REALLY WANTED\NSOMEONE TO TALK TO,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.69,0:15:02.44,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT THAT'S HARD TO DO WHEN\NNO ONE KNOWS WHAT YOU'RE SAYING.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.53,0:15:04.49,Main,,0,0,0,,IT WAS KIND OF A NIGHTMARE.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.82,0:15:08.83,Main,,0,0,0,,IT'S TRUE WHAT THEY SAY
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.91,0:15:11.41,Main,,0,0,0,,ABOUT FIRST IMPRESSIONS\NLASTING FOREVER.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.49,0:15:13.41,Main,,0,0,0,,I PROVED THAT THE DAY\NI SHOWED THEM
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.50,0:15:16.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I DIDN'T KNOW HOW TO WRITE\NMY OWN NAME.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.17,0:15:21.92,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( German accent )\NWAIT.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.00,0:15:26.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I'M SURE I NEVER\NCORRECTED THIS ONE MYSELF.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.13,0:15:30.01,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT WHO...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.10,0:15:31.51,Main,,0,0,0,,- SO CHECK IT OUT.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.60,0:15:33.02,Main,,0,0,0,,THE GUYS FROM AKEBONO JUNIOR\NHIGH WANT TO PLAY BASKETBALL
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.10,0:15:36.02,Main,,0,0,0,,FOR GRUB FROM\NTHE SCHOOL STORE.  YOU IN?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.10,0:15:37.64,Main,,0,0,0,,- HECK YEAH, I'M IN!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.73,0:15:39.48,Main,,0,0,0,,I HAVE, LIKE,\NNOTHING FOR A FOOD BUDGET.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.56,0:15:41.11,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'M IN TOO.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.19,0:15:42.57,Main,,0,0,0,,- WOULD YOU MIND\NIF I JOINED YOU GUYS?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.65,0:15:44.78,Main,,0,0,0,,PLAYING SOME BALL\NSOUNDS LIKE FUN.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:47.53,Main,,0,0,0,,- THAT'S WEIRD.\NWHEN DID THEY BECOME SO CLOSE?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.61,0:15:51.33,Main,,0,0,0,,- Hideyoshi: UH, I DON'T KNOW.\N- Akihisa: I GOT THIS.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.41,0:15:54.20,Main,,0,0,0,,( speaks French badly )
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.37,0:15:56.91,Main,,0,0,0,,AM I SAYING IT RIGHT?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.00,0:15:59.96,Main,,0,0,0,,( speaks French badly )
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.04,0:16:02.13,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT IS WITH HIM?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:04.84,Main,,0,0,0,,WHY DOES HE KEEP TALKING TO ME\NIN GIBBERISH?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.92,0:16:07.05,Main,,0,0,0,,NOW HE IS JUST\NMAKING FUN OF ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.13,0:16:10.05,Main,,0,0,0,,THE LEAST HE COULD DO IS\NGET MY NAME RIGHT.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.14,0:16:11.80,Main,,0,0,0,,MINAMI, NOT MONAMI, JERK.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.89,0:16:14.60,Main,,0,0,0,,IF YOU DON'T\NEVEN KNOW WHO I AM,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.68,0:16:16.73,Main,,0,0,0,,WHY TRY SO HARD TO UPSET ME?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.81,0:16:19.56,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( speaks French badly )
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.11,0:16:24.32,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}TU NE VOUDRAIS--{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.40,0:16:25.86,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( speaks German )
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.94,0:16:28.99,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU WANT TO SHAVE FUR\NOFF A BEAST?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.07,0:16:30.99,Main,,0,0,0,,- I SAY...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.07,0:16:33.87,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT A "SHE-MAN" YOU ARE?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.95,0:16:35.50,Main,,0,0,0,,AS IN-- WAIT.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.58,0:16:37.41,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU'RE SAYING\NYOU'RE A DUDE?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.50,0:16:38.87,Main,,0,0,0,,OH, THAT'S COOL, I GUESS.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.96,0:16:41.29,Main,,0,0,0,,- THIS BOY IS\NTHE BIGGEST IDIOT ON EARTH!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.38,0:16:43.92,Main,,0,0,0,,- THERE WAS SOMETHING IN THERE\NABOUT YOU BEING A SHITTY GUY.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.00,0:16:45.50,Main,,0,0,0,,GUESS YOU PISSED HER OFF, MAN.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.59,0:16:47.13,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH, REALLY?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.22,0:16:49.17,Main,,0,0,0,,- YEAH.  YOU THOUGHT A GIRL\NWAS ACTUALLY TELLING YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.26,0:16:51.26,Main,,0,0,0,,SHE WAS A GUY,\NAND DIDN'T EVEN QUESTION IT?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.34,0:16:53.68,Main,,0,0,0,,THAT'S HARSH, BRO.\N- I AM SO SORRY, SHIMADA!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.76,0:16:55.68,Main,,0,0,0,,I DIDN'T MEAN IT,\NAND IT HAS NOTHING TO DO
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.76,0:16:57.35,Main,,0,0,0,,WITH THE FACT THAT YOUR CHEST\NIS FREAKISHLY FLAT
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.43,0:17:00.81,Main,,0,0,0,,OR THAT MY ELBOWS ARE\NBEING TORN OUT OF THEIR SOCKETS!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.89,0:17:03.02,Main,,0,0,0,,- I MAY NOT UNDERSTAND\NEVERYTHING THEY'RE SAYING,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.11,0:17:05.23,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT I'M CERTAIN\NI HEARD "FLAT-CHESTED."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.32,0:17:07.23,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAT DID I EVER DO TO HIM?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.32,0:17:09.53,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU ARE A VERY BIG SHIT MAN!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.37,0:17:14.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I HATE THIS.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.24,0:17:15.74,Main,,0,0,0,,I HATE IT HERE.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.83,0:17:17.58,Main,,0,0,0,,I WISH I NEVER MOVED.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.66,0:17:20.66,Main,,0,0,0,,- HEY, SHIMADA.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.75,0:17:22.42,Main,,0,0,0,,JUST WANTED TO SAY I DON'T\NKNOW THAT IDIOT VERY WELL,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.50,0:17:24.38,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT I THINK\NHE MIGHT BE ALL RIGHT.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.46,0:17:25.96,Main,,0,0,0,,AND I ALSO THINK
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.05,0:17:27.67,Main,,0,0,0,,THAT YOU MIGHT BE FREAKING OUT\NA LITTLE TOO MUCH.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.76,0:17:29.30,Main,,0,0,0,,- ME?  WHY?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:33.76,Main,,0,0,0,,- I KNOW HE ACTS WEIRD\NWHEN HE TALKS TO YOU,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.85,0:17:35.18,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT WHAT HE'S SAYING IS NICE.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.24,0:17:59.20,Main,,0,0,0,,- SO THAT'S THE WORD\NFOR "IDIOT."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.29,0:18:01.04,Main,,0,0,0,,THAT'LL BE USEFUL AROUND HERE.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.58,0:18:07.13,Main,,0,0,0,,( speaks French )
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.21,0:18:09.42,Main,,0,0,0,,I CAN'T FIGURE IT OUT.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.51,0:18:13.59,Main,,0,0,0,,HE'S PROBABLY TRYING TO\NCONFUSE ME SO I'LL LOOK STUPID.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.68,0:18:16.01,Main,,0,0,0,,AS SOON AS I FIND IT,\NI'LL SAY SOMETHING
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.10,0:18:17.56,Main,,0,0,0,,JUST AS RUDE BACK.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.64,0:18:20.27,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( inaudible )
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.35,0:18:23.69,Main,,0,0,0,,- {\i1}"TU NE VOUDRAIS PAS.{\i0}\N{\i1}TU NE VOUDRAIS PAS..." {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.77,0:18:25.19,Main,,0,0,0,,WHERE IS IT?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.27,0:18:27.69,Main,,0,0,0,,UGH, THIS IS MAKING\NMY BRAIN HURT.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.77,0:18:30.90,Main,,0,0,0,,WHY CAN'T I FIND IT?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.98,0:18:34.53,Main,,0,0,0,,EVEN IF HE'S USING SLANG,\NSOMETHING SHOULD'VE POPPED UP.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.61,0:18:36.91,Main,,0,0,0,,AND DOES HE REALLY NOT KNOW\NMY NAME BY NOW
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.99,0:18:39.37,Main,,0,0,0,,OR IS HE CALLING ME "MONAMI"\NJUST TO BE ANNOYING?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.45,0:18:40.70,Main,,0,0,0,,WAIT A MINUTE.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.79,0:18:43.21,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( violin music playing )
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.14,0:18:58.64,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( gasps )
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.72,0:19:00.47,Main,,0,0,0,,HERE IT IS.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.35,0:19:07.44,Main,,0,0,0,,FRANCE.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.26,0:19:35.38,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"TU NE VOUDRAIS PAS{\i0}\N{\i1}DEVENIR MON AMIE."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.47,0:19:37.13,Main,,0,0,0,,SO IT ISN'T IN JAPANESE.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.22,0:19:39.55,Main,,0,0,0,,I BET HE WAS TRYING TO LOOK UP\NSOMETHING IN GERMAN,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.64,0:19:42.14,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT FOUND IT IN FRENCH\NON ACCIDENT.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.22,0:19:44.89,Main,,0,0,0,,WOW.\NHE REALLY IS AN IDIOT.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.94,0:19:48.69,Main,,0,0,0,,- Minami:\NAFTER I FIGURED THAT PART OUT,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.77,0:19:50.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I COULDN'T FIND\NA FRENCH-GERMAN DICTIONARY
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.65,0:19:52.36,Main,,0,0,0,,ANYWHERE IN THE LIBRARY.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.44,0:19:54.78,Main,,0,0,0,,I HAD TO TRANSLATE THE WHOLE\NTHING INTO ENGLISH FIRST
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.86,0:19:57.03,Main,,0,0,0,,AND THEN BACK INTO GERMAN.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.11,0:19:58.74,Main,,0,0,0,,I HAD NO IDEA IF\NI WAS SPELLING IT RIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.82,0:20:00.41,Main,,0,0,0,,OR EVEN PRONOUNCING IT\NWELL ENOUGH TO GUESS.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.71,0:20:08.92,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( German accent )\NTHERE.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.59,0:20:13.92,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"TU NE VOUDRAIS PAS" {\i0}\NIS SECOND PERSON.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.01,0:20:17.55,Main,,0,0,0,,IT SHOULD MEAN "COULD YOU."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.63,0:20:21.55,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"DEVENIR"{\i0} IS "BECOME."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.64,0:20:25.97,Main,,0,0,0,,HE WAS SAYING {\i1}"MON AMIE,"{\i0}\NNOT "MINAMI."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.06,0:20:30.40,Main,,0,0,0,,AND {\i1}"MON AMIE" {\i0}\NMEANS "MY FRIEND."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.48,0:20:33.02,Main,,0,0,0,,SO IF I PUT IT ALL TOGETHER,\NIT MEANS...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.11,0:20:38.36,Main,,0,0,0,,"COULD YOU BECOME MY FRIEND?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.45,0:20:41.28,Main,,0,0,0,,- {\i1}TU NE VOUDRAIS PAS{\i0}\N{\i1}DEVENIR MON AMIE?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.37,0:20:44.16,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}TU NE VOUDRAIS PAS{\i0}\N{\i1}DEVENIR MON AMIE.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.09,0:20:57.63,Main,,0,0,0,,- HE HAD TO GO THROUGH ALL THIS\NTO BE ABLE TO SAY IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.72,0:20:59.26,Main,,0,0,0,,HE LEARNED THE WRONG LANGUAGE
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.34,0:21:01.72,Main,,0,0,0,,FROM A COUNTRY\NHE'S NEVER BEEN TO.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.80,0:21:02.97,Main,,0,0,0,,HE DOESN'T EVEN\NWORK THAT HARD
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.05,0:21:05.93,Main,,0,0,0,,FOR THE CLASSES IN\NHIS OWN LANGUAGE.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.02,0:21:08.60,Main,,0,0,0,,HE'S NOT THAT SMART...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.68,0:21:10.89,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT HE TRIED.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.98,0:21:13.40,Main,,0,0,0,,HE TRIED SO HARD.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.24,0:21:19.95,Main,,0,0,0,,COULD YOU BECOME MY--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.03,0:21:21.20,Main,,0,0,0,,MY FRIEND?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.28,0:21:24.45,Main,,0,0,0,,OH, THAT IS SUCH A NICE WORDS!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.04,0:21:28.45,Main,,0,0,0,,I COULD.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.59,0:21:43.47,Main,,0,0,0,,GOOD MORNING, YOSHII!\NHOW ARE YOU?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.55,0:21:46.81,Main,,0,0,0,,- UH, MORNING, SHIMADA.\NNICE TO SEE YOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.93,0:21:52.14,Main,,0,0,0,,WHOA.  HI.\NWHAT'S UP, YOU ALL RIGHT?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.23,0:21:54.65,Main,,0,0,0,,- I WISH TO TELL YOU SOMETHING.\N- UH, 'KAY?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.73,0:21:57.23,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT A SHIT--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.32,0:21:59.07,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT'D I DO NOW?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.15,0:22:00.82,Main,,0,0,0,,I'M SO SORRY.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.90,0:22:02.03,Main,,0,0,0,,DID I DO SOMETHING\NTO UPSET YOU AGAIN?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.11,0:22:03.49,Main,,0,0,0,,- NO, I AM NOT MAD!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.57,0:22:06.49,Main,,0,0,0,,HOW DO YOU SAY...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.00,0:22:18.92,Main,,0,0,0,,"YOU WERE NOT A SHIT PERSON."\NYOU SEE...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.01,0:22:20.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I WAS.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.05,0:22:26.85,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( singing in Japanese )
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.27,0:23:53.81,Main,,0,0,0,,- Fukuhara:\NQUESTION NUMBER NINE:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.89,0:23:56.23,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAT DO YOU CALL THE ACTIONS\NBY GROUPS THAT REACH OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.31,0:23:59.36,Main,,0,0,0,,TO POLITICIANS\NIN ORDER TO INFLUENCE POLICIES?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.44,0:24:01.36,Main,,0,0,0,,- Minami: FLIRTING?\N- WHO'S YOUR DADDY?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.44,0:24:02.98,Main,,0,0,0,,- Akihisa: NEXT TIME:\NME, ROMANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.07,0:24:04.23,Main,,0,0,0,,AND NEGOTIATION SKILLS.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.32,0:24:06.20,Main,,0,0,0,,- Fukuhara:\NTHIS WILL BE ON THE TEST.
